    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, providing a direct mechanical connection to the M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains rigid with a reinforced rear subframe, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to maintain peak torque across the power band. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, preserving the platform's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and telepathic steering feedback. While the aesthetic reflects honest use, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for spirited performance.",
