      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury performance and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical of a well-traveled car but well-preserved overall. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring premium leather seating that has been conditioned monthly to prevent cracking. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and navigation system, are in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent fluid flush and brake pad replacement. The tires currently show approximately 70% tread life remaining, ensuring you won't need an immediate trip to the shop. This is a reliable, honest vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
